ok so i try to stay out of drama and it never works!!!! AH! High school is fun but so dumb at the same time! Anyway i broke up with alex liek what 2 weeks ago, well he still makes me feel bad about it! goodness! anyway ive been talking to steven manson and i like him only he doesnt go to my school but hey i can live with liking someone that doesnt go to my school! hes my friend JD's cousin. anyway it can be very benifitial because i will not get sick of him ALWAYS being around me, and when i do see him itill be "special" or whatever and it wont really get old. so hey thats pretty cool RiGhT?? we talked 3 hours last night... fun stuff! well anyway tonight im going to a dance yay! fun and tomorrow family christmas party!!!!! lol thats always fun. well better get going
